txt.en: The nesting grounds of Nathból can be found in Elderslade.\n\nYou should defeat Wyrmsgráf breeders found at Nathból.
The nesting grounds of Nathból can be found in Elderslade.\n\nYou should defeat Wyrmsgráf breeders found at Nathból.
You have defeated many Wyrmsgráf breeders at Nathból.

The worm nesting grounds of Nathból prevent those who seek to journey up the river towards Wyrmsgráf. If some of the worms breeding at Nathból are defeated, perhaps the route towards Wyrmsgráf will become safer to travel.
